H(x,x';\tau) \to V(x)\, e^{-\tau \Delta_x} \, V^{-1}(x)\, \delta(x-x') =
V(x)\, e^{-\tau \Delta_x} \, \delta(x-x') \, V^{-1}(x') =
V(x)\, H(x,x';\tau)  \, V^{-1}(x')  \,,
\

\begin{equation}
